  			</div>
  		</div><div>
  			<div id="item-2060"><p>We&#8217;re having a cool and rainy day here too. Rhubarb crisp sounds perfect.</p>
<p><span class="caps">BTW</span>, that sounds like some great birthday dinner. Calvin is a lucky boy.</p></div>
